      <title>德国通过32亿欧元法案减轻企业负担</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/germany-passes-3-2-billion-bill-to-ease-burden-on-companies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国议会上院通过了一项淡化法案，为企业提供 32 亿欧元（合 35 亿美元）的减税措施，结束了联合政府、联邦各州和反对党之间数月的争执。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/germany-passes-3-2-billion-bill-to-ease-burden-on-companies</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 11:34:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
